type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}]},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"link","title":"the following guidelines","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"the following guidelines","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"}}}